node_6.description: This is Klaus Mueller's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am, Go to the library at Oak Hill College, and work on the research paper from 8:00 am to 12:00 pm, eat at Hobbs Cafe at 12:00, which will give you more energy and help you continue working until 4:00 pm, After lunch, Klaus will work at the library until 5 pm, Klaus then will have some free time until dinner, Klaus eats dinner around 5 pm., After dinner, Klaus will spend time with friends until 7:00 pm.
